{"tid":1448704,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場 An eye for an eye","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:12.000Z","uid":46814,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"56a1a9203c022583f50cbe043ffb05d3114cd7ff","tid":1448704,"uid":46814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:20.000Z","msg":"無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=60c14ec0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n<br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=bbfaa38d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"34bf97d4f077c1c8ab6fcc198d181e1322654a64","tid":1448704,"uid":148152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場"},{"pid":"2d87b7ff6226ae915de908009852cede7fa1e306","tid":1448704,"uid":33543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQZURP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQZURP7.jpg&h=e8ff53ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvexDu8